<BaseLayout
  title="Rentar — Fuel Catalyst Technology & Emissions Reduction"
  description="Rentar® is the exclusive worldwide commercial rights holder for the Rentar Fuel Catalyst. Learn how to verify whether a company is authorized to sell genuine Rentar Fuel Catalyst products and how to report unauthorized representation."
>

<!-- ====== HERO ====== -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-tag">Patented Fuel Catalyst Technology</p>
    <h1>Proven combustion <strong>efficiency.</strong><br>Measurable emissions <strong>reduction.</strong></h1>
    <p>Rentar<sup style="font-size:0.55em;">®</sup> is the exclusive worldwide commercial rights holder for the Rentar Fuel Catalyst — deployed across mining, marine, agriculture, oil and gas, power generation, and heavy transport for over two decades.</p>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Talk to our team</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ====== STATS ====== -->
<div class="stats">
  <div class="stats-grid">
    <div><div class="stat-number">33</div><div class="stat-label">international<br>patents</div></div>
    <div><div class="stat-number">20+</div><div class="stat-label">countries<br>deployed</div></div>
    <div><div class="stat-number">1M+</div><div class="stat-label">engines<br>compatible</div></div>
    <div><div class="stat-number">10%</div><div class="stat-label">average fuel<br>efficiency gain</div></div>
    <div><div class="stat-number">2003</div><div class="stat-label">year Rentar<br>was founded</div></div>
    <div><div class="stat-number">0</div><div class="stat-label">moving parts<br>in the catalyst</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ====== COMPANY ====== -->
<section class="section manifesto" id="company">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <p class="section-label">The Company</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Built on a simple idea: better combustion means less fuel</h2>
    <div class="manifesto-block">
      <p>Rentar<sup style="font-size:0.55em;">®</sup> Environmental Solutions has spent over two decades developing, testing, and deploying fuel catalyst technology in the world's most demanding industrial environments. From open-pit mines in Brazil to offshore platforms in the Atlantic, from agricultural fleets across the Midwest to marine vessels transiting global shipping lanes — Rentar technology is proven where fuel consumption matters most.</p>
      <p class="manifesto-highlight">33 international patents. No moving parts. No electronics. No maintenance. Just measurable results.</p>
      <p>Rentar holds the exclusive worldwide commercial rights to manufacture, market, sell, and deploy the Rentar Fuel Catalyst across industrial, marine, mining, power generation, and transportation markets.</p>
    </div>
    <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline">The Rentar story</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ====== TECHNOLOGY ====== -->
<section class="section section-light" id="technology">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split">
      <div class="split-image" style="background:transparent; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; border-radius:4px; overflow:hidden;">
        <iframe src="/images/rentar_catalyst_animation" style="width:100%; max-width:960px; height:520px; border:0;" title="Rentar fuel catalyst animation" loading="lazy"></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="split-content">
        <p class="section-label">Core Technology</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Rentar Fuel Catalyst</h2>
        <p class="section-text">A passive in-line fuel catalyst installed upstream of the engine. Conditions fuel at the molecular level to improve combustion efficiency. No moving parts. No electronics. No maintenance. Protected by 33 international patents and deployable on over one million compatible engine configurations worldwide.</p>
        <a href="/technology" class="btn btn-outline">Explore the technology</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

